ct_count\":\"10\",\"seo_url\":\"Content-Writing\",\"updatedate\":\"2016-08-03 20:56:44\",\"category_id\":\"2\",\"islocal\":\"0\",\"isremote\":\"1\",\"descr\":\"Content writing is providing relevant information for products and services on a website. This information comes in different forms such as marketing, newsletters or speeches. The purpose of writing is to help many people know as much as possible about a product before they buy it.Hiring a professional for content writing is a great option since the person knows how to write with skills that can sell, inform and meet your company\\\\'s needs. A person who can bring life to your company\\\\'s marketing, make sure your projects are completed on time and at very low cost. An expert in content writing knows the tone, styles and many more and can produce perfect writing that gets results at the end of the day.     A freelancer increases productivity of your company. When you know that the person handling your content writing projects is an expert, you can dedicate more time to other aspects of your business. It does not matter what kind of content you need written, as an experienced freelancer can do it all. After hiring a freelancer, the bottom line will be simple, your content writing will be professionally written at the exact time and at very affordable costs. You can save money on your content writing.\",\"seotext\":\"\\u003Cp\\u003ESometimes, when words just aren\\u2019t your thing, you need the services of an experienced and creative content writer.\\u003C\\/p\\u003E\\u003Cp\\u003EContent writers can assist with a range of writing tasks from corporate style writing of your business documents, reports and corporate profiles right through to creating engaging EDM\\u2019s and social media posts that engage with your audience.\\u003C\\/p\\u003E\\u003Cp\\u003EThese days\\u2019 businesses have had to up the ante when it comes to content and with more and more business pushed into the digital realm clients and potential customers are demanding regular and engaging content by way of articles, blogs, and social media.\\u00a0It can be a challenge for businesses to keep up their marketing and brand awareness especially with the demands of online marketing and engaging a content writing professional to write web content and help with your marketing writing for your business will save you time and keep your business top of mind for your customers.\\u003C\\/p\\u003E\\u003Cp\\u003EContent writing professionals can write any content for your business needs, the list is exhaustive however here are a few things content writers can assist with outlined below:\\u003C\\/p\\u003E\\u003Cul\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003ENewsletters\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EArticles \\u00a0\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EBooks &amp; eBooks \\u00a0\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EGhostwriting\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EPowerPoint\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EPress releases\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EReport writing\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EResumes\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EScreenwriting\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003ESpeech writing\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003ESlogans\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003ETaglines\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003ETravel writing\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003ESocial media posts\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003Cli\\u003EProduct descriptions\\u003C\\/li\\u003E\\u003C\\/ul\\u003E\\u003Cp\\u003EEngaging a content writer puts you in contact with some of the best wordsmiths in the business. You can engage a freelancer content writer who specialises in just about every area; a quick search through freelancer.com will provide you with content writers who specialize in writing for all industries, in all languages and all purposes.\\u003C\\/p\\u003E\\u003Cp\\u003EFreelance content writers are affordable, reliable and focused on providing quality content for individuals and companies across the world. Writers can enjoy the freedom of working at a p